%% Triple-Pass Port Killer 상태머신 (plan.md §2.2)
%% internal/portkiller가 이 다이어그램의 상태/전이와 1:1 일치해야 함
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> GracefulSent
    GracefulSent --> Polling: signal dispatched
    Polling --> Polling: port still occupied (count < 3)
    Polling --> Released: port free
    Polling --> ResolveBlocker: 3 polls done, still occupied
    ResolveBlocker --> ForceKill: same-target PID resolved
    ResolveBlocker --> CrossTargetReport: cross-target PID
    ResolveBlocker --> UnknownBlocker: resolution failed
    ForceKill --> Released: kill success
    ForceKill --> UnknownBlocker: kill failed (privilege)
    CrossTargetReport --> [*]: surface to UI, no kill
    UnknownBlocker --> [*]: surface to UI, modal
    Released --> [*]
